ad to face Karolina for elimination. Margaux and Zi Lin were saved, while Stephanie and Jocelyn were eliminated.\n:* In episode 8, Zilin, Devyn, and Margaux were put through to the final runway show while Ebony was eliminated.\n\n=== Campaigns===\n* Episode 1: Natural beauty shots; self-administered 'transformations' with accessories from [[DKNY]] (casting)\n* Episode 2: Grouped in a [[shipyard]] for [[W (magazine)|W Magazine]]\n* Episode 3: Commercial with Cosabella lingerie in teams\n* Episode 4: Kleinfeld bridal dress fashion show\n* Episode 5: Look-books for Marshall's in teams\n* Episode 6: Self-directed commercials for Opensky.com\n* Episode 7: [[Red carpet|Red Carpet]] interviews conducted by [[Wendy Williams]]\n* Episode 8: [[Ulta Beauty|ULTA Beauty]] beauty shots\n\n== Television ratings ==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"width:72%;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" width=7% | No. in<br />series\n! scope=\"col\" width=7% | No. in<br />season\n!  Title\n! scope=\"col\" width=20% | Original air date\n! scope=\"col\" width=14% | U.S. viewers<br/>(million)\n|-\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber   = 1\n |EpisodeNumber2  = 1\n |Title           = The Fight to Make the Final 12\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2013|2|5}}\n |Viewers         = 0.34<ref>{{cite web|title=Tuesday's Cable Ratings: \"Tosh.0\" Returns, \"Hardcore Pawn\" Wraps on Top|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/ratings/2013/02/06/tuesdays-cable-ratings-tosh0-returns-hardcore-pawn-wraps-on-top-287511/cable_20130205/|publisher=The Futon Critic|accessdate=February 14, 2013}}</ref>\n |LineColor       = A780FB\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber   = 2\n |EpisodeNumber2  = 2\n |Title           = Game On!\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2013|2|12}}\n |Viewers         = 0.51<ref>{{cite web|title=Tuesday's Cable Ratings: \"Tosh.0\" Tops Demos, Westminster Dog Show Leads Viewers|url=http://thefutoncritic.com/ratings/2013/02/13/tuesdays-cable-ratings-tosh0-tops-demos-westminster-dog-show-leads-viewers-364410/cable_20130212/|publisher=The Futon Critic|accessdate=February 14, 2013}}</ref>\n |LineColor       = A780FB\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber   = 3\n |EpisodeNumber2  = 3\n |Title           = Model Warfare\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2013|2|19}}\n |Viewers         = 0.46<ref>{{cite web|title=Tuesday's Cable Ratings: \"Tosh.0,\" \"Pretty Little Liars\" Top Demo Race|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/ratings/2013/02/21/tuesdays-cable-ratings-tosh0-pretty-little-liars-top-demo-race-765314/cable_20130219/|publisher=the Futon Critic|accessdate=February 22, 2013}}</ref>\n |LineColor       = A780FB\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber   = 4\n |EpisodeNumber2  = 4\n |Title           = Falling From Grace\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2013|2|26}}\n |Viewers         = 0.56<ref>{{cite web|title=Tuesday's Cable Ratings: \"Tosh.0,\" \"Pretty Little Liars\" Lead Demo Race|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/ratings/2013/02/27/tuesdays-cable-ratings-tosh0-pretty-little-liars-lead-demo-race-400022/cable_20130226/|publisher=the Futon Critic|accessdate=February 28, 2013}}</ref>\n |LineColor       = A780FB\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber   = 5\n |EpisodeNumber2  = 5\n |Title           = We Are the Most Miserable Team Here\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2013|3|5}}\n |Viewers         = 0.50<ref>{{cite web|title=Tuesday's Cable Ratings: TNT Tops Charts with Lakers/Thunder|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/ratings/2013/03/06/tuesdays-cable-ratings-tnt-tops-charts-with-lakers-thunder-577514/cable_20130305/|publisher=the Futon Critic|accessdate=March 7, 2013}}</ref>\n |LineColor       = A780FB\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber   = 6\n |EpisodeNumber2  = 6\n |Title           = Every Rose Has its Thorns\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2013|3|12}}\n |Viewers         = 0.45<ref>{{cite web|title=Tuesday's Cable Ratings: \"Tosh.0\" Reclaims Demo Crown, \"Liars\" Tops Viewers|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/ratings/2013/03/13/tuesdays-cable-ratings-tosh0-reclaims-demo-